# Scholar Enhancement Tutorial Demo 1: Help System
# Shows how to access help for Scholar Enhancement features

Output docs/demos/tutorials/scholar-01-help.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20

# Show the command
Type "teach slides --help"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

# Scroll to show Universal Flags section
Type "# Universal Flags section shows style presets and content flags"
Sleep 2s

# Clear for next demo
Sleep 1s
